@startuml MQTT Service Architecture
!theme plain
title ARM Game - MQTT Service Interactions

' -- Participants -----------------------------
participant "Game Console\n(real-game-with-feeling.sh)" as Game #LightBlue
participant "Scoreboard RGB\n(scoreboard/mqtt_consumer.py)" as ScoreboardRGB #LightGreen
participant "Flip Digits\n(flippies/mqtt_consumer.py)" as Flippies #LightGreen
participant "Arm Control\n(motion/arm_mqtt_consumer.py)" as Arm #Orange
participant "Target Blinkies\n(motion/target_blinkies_\nmqtt_consumer.py)" as Blinkies #Orange
participant "Target Scoring\n(motion/target_scoring_\nmqtt_consumer.py)" as Scoring #Orange
participant "Target Movement\n(motion/target_movement_\nmqtt_consumer.py)" as Movement #Orange
participant "Cowbell\n(mqtt_cowbell.sh)" as Cowbell #Plum
participant "Ding Ding\n(mqtt_dingding.sh)" as DingDing #Plum

== Pre-Game ==

Game -> Scoring : /targets/{1..8}/disable
Game -> Cowbell : /scoreboard/cowbell

== Game Start ==

Game -> Flippies : /scoreboard/digits/clear

Game -> ScoreboardRGB : /scoreboard/rgb/start_timer
Game -> Blinkies : /scoreboard/rgb/start_timer
Game -> Scoring : /scoreboard/rgb/start_timer
Game -> DingDing : /scoreboard/rgb/start_timer

Game -> Arm : /motion/motion/start

Game -> Movement : /target_movement/start

Game -> Scoring : /scoreboard/player_info

== Gameplay Loop ==

note over Blinkies : Randomly raises, enables,\ndisables, and lowers targets

Blinkies -> Scoring : /targets/{id}/up
Blinkies -> Scoring : /targets/{id}/enable
Blinkies -> Scoring : /targets/{id}/disable
Blinkies -> Scoring : /targets/{id}/down
Blinkies -> Scoring : /targets/{id}/home

note over Scoring : Polls targets via serial.\nPublishes score on hit.

Scoring -> Cowbell : /targets/{id}/hit
Scoring -> Flippies : /scoreboard/digits/set_number

== Timer Expires ==

note over ScoreboardRGB : Timer reaches 0:00

ScoreboardRGB -> Game : /scoreboard/timer/game_over\n(unblocks mosquitto_sub -C 1)
ScoreboardRGB -> Blinkies : /scoreboard/timer/game_over
ScoreboardRGB -> Scoring : /scoreboard/timer/game_over
ScoreboardRGB -> DingDing : /scoreboard/timer/game_over

note over Scoring : Records score to SQLite.\nRings bell if high score.
note over Blinkies : Disables & homes all targets.

== Game Over ==

Game -> ScoreboardRGB : /scoreboard/rgb/game_over
Game -> Arm : /motion/motion/stop
Game -> Movement : /target_movement/stop
Game -> Scoring : /targets/{1..8}/disable

@enduml
